---
title: Creamy Chicken & Chickpea Stew with Roasted Kumara & Couscous
description: When we first tried this bright burst of goodness, we all agreed it had that "hug in a bowl" kind of feeling. There's wholesome chicken,
chickpeas, kumara and silverbeet, plus a sublime, lightly spiced creamy sauce that soaks into the couscous. Snuggle up and enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-coconut-chickpea-stew-0e70cd49.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/creamy-coconut-chickpea-stew-608a450f74bc255a4867904e-e01fe30c.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/creamy-chicken-and-chickpea-stew-608a450f74bc255a4867904e
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 40 minutes
nutrition:
  fat: 57.3 g
